[There are of 137 154 suspected measles cases reported in the DR Congo this year (2019) and we have more than 4 months to go to the end of the year. This is a consequence of so many problems in the country, including Ebola and all the other issues this population faces, as listed above. It is truly a horrific situation and definitely a humanitarian crisis that the world should rally around to do what they can to relieve the suffering of the Congolese people. - Mod.LK

